{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, sentiment analysis has been effectively integrated into Seq2Seq models to enhance the sentiment appropriateness of Chatbot responses as for instance in [24].",
    "For managing dialogue flow, both rule-based approaches, which follow predefined rules, and data-driven approaches, which leverage dialog datasets to train models, were explored.",
    "Furthermore in [25] the authors developed a multi-turn dialogue management system using reinforcement learning to maintain emotional consistency over extended interactions [25].",
    "Additionally, in [26] the authors focused on generating empathetic responses in open-domain dialogues by fine-tuning pre-trained language models on empathetic dialogue datasets [26].",
    "To enhance context-awareness in emotional Chatbots, in [27] the authors integrated memory networks, allowing the system to track and utilize conversation history for better emotion recognition and response generation [27]."
  ]
}